<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TMaL27">
<l>kuraṅkukaḷ malaiyai nūkkak kuḷittuttām puraṇṭiṭ ṭōṭit</l>
<l>taraṅkanī raṭaikka luṟṟa calamilā vaṇilum pōlēṉ</l>
<l>maraṅkaḷpōl valiya neñca vañcaṉēṉ neñcu taṉṉā</l>
<l>laraṅkaṉārk kāṭcey yātē yaḷiyattē ṉayarkkiṉ ṟēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I am not like the malice-free squirrels,</l>
<l>Which bathed [in the sea], rolled over [the sands], ran,</l>
<l>And began to block the wavy ocean,</l>
<l>as the monkeys shoved the hills.</l>
<l>I, a fraudulent person with a heart hardened like trees,</l>
<l>Have not served [the Lord] of Raṅgam with [my] heart,</l>
<l>I, a wretched person, have forgotten [Him].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
